  * http://www.physics.utah.edu/~detar/scidac/qio_2p3.pdf
  * http://ildg.sasr.edu.au/Plone/ildg/ildg-standards/file-format-standards/ildg-file-format.pdf
  * http://cd.nersc.gov/utilities/format-v103.ps.gz
  * http://fermiqcd.net
